133
00:12:04.613 --> 00:12:06.949
<i>Bersama Yeldon dan Chantel!</i>

134
00:12:07.282 --> 00:12:12.329
<i>Bersama Murray semestinya,</i>
<i>Ellis Drane dan kumpulan jaznya.</i>


135
00:12:12.413 --> 00:12:14.915
<i>Sekarang tanpa</i>
<i>melengahkan masa lagi...</i>


136
00:12:14.999 --> 00:12:18.503
Murray Franklin!

137
00:12:30.223 --> 00:12:31.683
Terima kasih.

138
00:12:33.268 --> 00:12:34.477
Terima kasih.

139
00:12:34.978 --> 00:12:36.897
Penonton kita malam ini nampak hebat.

140
00:12:37.439 --> 00:12:39.066
Murray!

141
00:12:39.191 --> 00:12:40.984
Terima kasih.

142
00:12:41.401 --> 00:12:42.736
Terima kasih.

143
00:12:43.070 --> 00:12:47.283
Semua orang sudah dengar
tentang tikus kebal di Gotham, bukan?


144
00:12:48.242 --> 00:12:51.746
Hari ini, datuk bandar kata
dia ada penyelesaiannya.


145
00:12:51.829 --> 00:12:53.122
Dah sedia?

146
00:12:53.414 --> 00:12:54.582
Kucing kebal.

147
00:12:59.295 --> 00:13:00.880
Saya benar-benar maksudkan...

148
00:13:00.963 --> 00:13:02.590
Saya sayang awak, Murray!

149
00:13:04.008 --> 00:13:05.343
Saya sayang awak juga.

150
00:13:07.178 --> 00:13:09.055
Bobby, boleh nyalakan lampu?

151
00:13:09.180 --> 00:13:10.932
Siapa kata tadi? Awak?

152
00:13:11.182 --> 00:13:12.392
Awak nak berdiri?

153
00:13:12.601 --> 00:13:13.977
Berdirilah.

154
00:13:14.352 --> 00:13:15.479
Hei.

155
00:13:20.817 --> 00:13:22.277
Siapa nama awak?

156
00:13:23.028 --> 00:13:25.239
Hai, Murray.
Saya Arthur.


157
00:13:25.322 --> 00:13:26.782
