1091
01:40:34.983 --> 01:40:37.485
Okey, saya ada satu.

1092
01:40:40.530 --> 01:40:42.574
Ketuk!

1093
01:40:43.283 --> 01:40:44.618
Awak terpaksa tengok buku?

