1214
01:53:44.723 --> 01:53:46.683
Awak nak beritahu saya jenaka itu?

1215
01:53:53.065 --> 01:53:54.525
Awak takkan faham.

1216
01:54:06.746 --> 01:54:08.331
<i>Itulah kehidupan.</i>

1217
01:54:10.124 --> 01:54:13.002
<i>Walaupun ia lucu...</i>

1218
01:54:14.254 --> 01:54:16.464
<i>ada orang yang seronok...</i>

1219
01:54:17.007 --> 01:54:19.509
<i>memusnahkan impian.</i>

1220
01:54:20.677 --> 01:54:24.431
<i>Tapi aku tak biarkan</i>
<i>ia buat aku sedih.</i>


1221
01:54:26.183 --> 01:54:31.313
<i>Kerana dunia ini tetap berputar.</i>

